OL,3,CFears 'outdated' divorce laws are
OL,4,Cbeing exploited by abusers
OL,6,FThere are fresh calls from Jersey
OL,7,Fcampaigners to update the island's
OL,8,F"restrictive and outdated" divorce
OL,9,Flaws.
OL,11,FThe rules currently dictate that
OL,12,Fcouples who both want to separate must
OL,13,Fbe apart for at least a year before
OL,14,Fthey can initiate divorce proceedings.
OL,16,FCouples must also be married for at
OL,17,Fleast three years before they can file
OL,18,Ffor divorce.
