OL,3,CFears 'outdated' divorce laws are
OL,4,Cbeing exploited by abusers
OL,6,FIt puts the island out of step with
OL,7,FGuernsey, which changed its laws last
OL,8,Fyear.
OL,10,FFor those leaving abusive
OL,11,Frelationships, this can prolong a
OL,12,Fpainful process.
OL,14,F'Claire', not her real name, claims
OL,15,Fshe left her husband due to abuse, but
OL,16,Fhad to wait two years before finally
OL,17,Fbeing able to officially separate.
