OL,3,CFears 'outdated' divorce laws are
OL,4,Cbeing exploited by abusers
OL,6,FClaire says it makes moving on
OL,7,F"impossible", adding: "The divorce
OL,8,Fthat you want you can't have, and
OL,9,Fduring that time, you're still
OL,10,Fconnected to that person.
OL,12,F"It's the last thing that you need or
OL,13,Fwant in your life, and during that
OL,14,Fwaiting period, there is no moving on."
OL,16,FJersey's law was made in 1949, and
OL,17,Funlike in Guernsey and the UK, it does
OL,18,Fnot have a 'no-fault' option, which
OL,19,Fallows spouses to end their marriage
OL,20,Fsimply because they want to.
