OL,3,CFears 'outdated' divorce laws are
OL,4,Cbeing exploited by abusers
OL,6,FTwo people can separate if certain
OL,7,Fcriteria are met, which include
OL,8,Ffinding fault or a period of
OL,9,Fseparation ranging from a year to two
OL,10,Fyears, depending on circumstances.
OL,12,FThere are concerns that the law is
OL,13,Fbeing manipulated by abusers to
OL,14,Femotionally harm their spouses and
OL,15,Fchildren.
