OL,3,CFears 'outdated' divorce laws are
OL,4,Cbeing exploited by abusers
OL,6,F"The other victims in this are the
OL,7,Fchildren who often end up being pawns
OL,8,Fin the family court system and victims
OL,9,Fof coercively controlling, abusive
OL,10,Fpartners.
OL,12,F"Of course, it's not just women who
OL,13,Fmay be victims in that regard; it can
OL,14,Fbe men.
OL,16,F"The fact is, coercive control is
OL,17,Fillegal in Jersey; it's just not
OL,18,Fillegal in our divorce laws, so it's
OL,19,Fjust vital that those divorce laws do
OL,20,Fcatch up."
