OL,3,CFears 'outdated' divorce laws are
OL,4,Cbeing exploited by abusers
OL,6,FThe Justice Minister explains: "It
OL,7,Fwill reflect the principle of 'no-
OL,8,Ffault' divorce, wherein two people can
OL,9,Fsimply choose to divorce without
OL,10,Fhaving to cite any cause for the
OL,11,Fbreakdown of their marriage.
OL,13,F"The draft law, if approved, would
OL,14,Falso implement a previous States
OL,15,FAssembly in principle decision to
OL,16,Fupdate the divorce process in the
OL,17,Ffollowing areas: removing the need for
OL,18,Fthree years of marriage before
OL,19,Fdivorce, introducing joint filing for
OL,20,Fdivorce, and removing the ability to
OL,21,Fcontest a divorce.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/10
